Happy Philthy Friday! Shout out to one of my clients who I’ve been training for over ten years. This awesome guy is turning 70 this October. @frankgrenci has hit a new personal best on his bench press. 225lbs 💪🏾 I love it when others motivate and inspire me to be better. Happy Mother’s Day to the most amazing mommy ever!! Amber Rose 🌹 you have taken on the hardest role of your life, and I must say that nobody tops you as a mother. I feel that you are making my mother so proud that she’s sprinkling her approval over you everyday. 🦋 We can’t thank you enough for your hard work, creativity, compassion and love that you show us all. ❤️ There isn’t a book on being the perfect mother, but you are leading the way with your examples. In the last eight years you’ve become a bonus mom and you’ve given our girls a little brother. I appreciate you, I cherish you and I thank you for everything my love. I hope you get caught up on some much needed rest. 🥰❤️😉 Happy Mother’s Day to all of you awesome moms! 🫶🏾
#happymothersday #mommabear #mommyiswatchingfromheaven
